OL,3,CScouts referred to police as inquest
OL,4,Cfinds boy was unlawfully killed
OL,6,FThe Scout Association has been
OL,7,Freferred to police for investigation
OL,8,Fduring an inquest which concluded a
OL,9,Fteenager who died on a Scout trip was
OL,10,Funlawfully killed.
OL,12,FBen Leonard, 16, from Stockport,
OL,13,FGreater Manchester, suffered a serious
OL,14,Fhead injury when he fell about 200ft
OL,15,Fat Great Orme in Llandudno, North
OL,16,FWales.
OL,18,FHe died while on a trip with the
OL,19,FReddish Explorer Scouts from
OL,20,FStockport, Greater Manchester, on
OL,21,FAugust 26 2018.
