OL,6,FThe law prevents inquest juries from
OL,7,Fnaming any individual in conclusions.
OL,9,FDuring the inquest the Scout leader on
OL,10,Fthe trip, Sean Glaister, declined to
OL,11,Fanswer a series of questions from Ben
OL,12,FRichmond KC, lawyer for Fieldfisher,
OL,13,Fthe law firm representing Ben's
OL,14,Ffamily. Mary Carr was named as the
OL,15,Fassistant scout leader on the trip.
