OL,3,CScouts referred to police as inquest
OL,4,Cfinds boy was unlawfully killed
OL,6,FDavid Pojur, assistant coroner for
OL,7,FNorth Wales east and central, has
OL,8,Freferred The Scout Association and an
OL,9,Femployee, who cannot be named by court
OL,10,Forder, to North Wales Police to
OL,11,Finvestigate for conspiracy to pervert
OL,12,Fthe course of justice. No further
OL,13,Fdetails on that matter can be reported.
OL,15,FJurors were not told of the police
OL,16,Freferral and the media had been
OL,17,Fordered not to report it until the
OL,18,Fjury reached their conclusions.
