OL,6,FLawyers for The Scout Association and
OL,7,Fseveral other individuals applied to
OL,8,Fextend the ban indefinitely on
OL,9,Freporting of the police referral.
OL,11,FThe application was refused by the
OL,12,Fcoroner following an application by PA
OL,13,Fnews agency, the BBC and The North
OL,14,FWales Pioneer newspaper.
OL,16,FAround 500,000 young people and
OL,17,F145,000 adult volunteers take part in
OL,18,FScouting projects and activities each
OL,19,Fweek, according to the association's
OL,20,Fown figures.
