OL,6,FAt the beginning of the inquest, the
OL,7,Fthird after two previous inquests were
OL,8,Faborted, The Scout Association for the
OL,9,Ffirst time publicly apologised and
OL,10,Faccepted responsibility for Ben's
OL,11,Fdeath.
OL,13,FBut his tearful mother, Jackie
OL,14,FLeonard, told the hearing their
OL,15,Fapology was five-and-a-half years too
OL,16,Flate and the treatment of her family
OL,17,Fhad been "disgusting".
OL,19,FBen's mum accuses the Scout
OL,20,FAssociation of trying to sweep her
OL,21,Fson's death "under the carpet"
