OL,6,FShe added: "Like we didn't matter and
OL,7,Flike Ben didn't matter."
OL,9,FShe described her son as a
OL,10,F"thoughtful, very funny, extremely
OL,11,Fwitty" boy who joined the Beavers aged
OL,12,Ffive and was an avid reader and film
OL,13,Fbuff and planned to study TV and film
OL,14,Fat college.
OL,16,FBut Mrs Leonard said The Scout
OL,17,FAssociation had tried to portray her
OL,18,Fson as a "wild child", taking a
OL,19,F"defensive" attitude and until their
OL,20,Fapology had never accepted being at
OL,21,Ffault.
