OL,6,FThe inquest also heard Ben's family
OL,7,Fwere lied to as the Scout Association
OL,8,Fwas worried about "reputational
OL,9,Fdamage".
OL,11,FAn initial inquest into the
OL,12,Fyoungster's death was held in February
OL,13,F2020 at Ruthin Coroner's Court but the
OL,14,Fjury was discharged by Mr Pojur, who
OL,15,Fsaid the Scout Association had failed
OL,16,Fto provide the court with full
OL,17,Finformation and "created a misleading
OL,18,Fimpression".
