OL,6,FThe witness agreed The Scout
OL,7,FAssociation never monitored his
OL,8,Factivities or ensured any training he
OL,9,Fwas supposed to undergo had ever been
OL,10,Fdone.
OL,12,FMr Richmond added: "They have hung you
OL,13,Fout to dry, haven't they?"
OL,15,F"Yeh," Mr Glaister said, "This could
OL,16,Fhave happened to any of the leaders on
OL,17,Fany of the trips we went on."
