OL,6,FAs an organisation we are committed to
OL,7,Flearning. The jury heard how in this
OL,8,Finstance the local leaders did not
OL,9,Ffollow our safety rules and processes.
OL,10,FAs a result of Ben's tragic death in
OL,11,F2018, we have already made many
OL,12,Fchanges to our risk assessments,
OL,13,Fsafety rules, training and support we
OL,14,Fgive our volunteers."
OL,16,FShe added: "Keeping young people safe
OL,17,Ffrom harm remains our number one
OL,18,Fpriority at scouts. We emphatically
OL,19,Frefute allegations made in court about
OL,20,Fany criminal action on behalf of The
OL,21,FScout Association."
